This directory (KIM_API) contains the openkim-api service routines and related
files.

The contents of the directory are as follows (before any compilation if
performed):

KIM_API.cpp
     C++ implementations for core service routines and methods.

KIM_API.h
     C++ Header file for KIM API service classes, routines and methods.

KIM_API_C.cpp
     Implementation of C-style interface for the KIM API.

KIM_API_C.h
     Header for C-style interface for KIM API service routines.

KIM_API_DIRS.h
     Header file defining a routine to supply directory locations to be searched
     by the API.

KIM_API_Description.txt
     Description of KIM API service routines.

KIM_API_F.F90
     Implementation of DEPRECATED Fortran-style interface for KIM API.

KIM_API_F03.F03
     Implementation of Fortran 2003-style interface for KIM API.

KIM_API_F03_Helper.F03
     Implementation of helper routines for the Fortran 2003-style interface.

KIM_API_status.h
     Header file defining the KIM API status codes.

KIM_AUX.cpp
     C++ implementation file containing auxiliary routines, including
     the native process_dEdr and process_d2Edr2 functions.

KIM_AUX.h
     Header file declaring the auxiliary routines.

Makefile
     Make file for compiling and building KIM_API

README
     This file.

Unit_Handling.cpp
     C++ implementation file defining the unit handling capabilities of the KIM
     API

Unit_Handling.h
     Header file declaring the unit handling functions.

openkim-api-descriptor-file-match.cpp
     A helper application that takes a Model descriptor file and a Test
     descriptor file and prints out either MATCH or NOMATCH.

standard.kim
     kim descriptor file with description of all standard variables.

